body:
Huhu

Last night I had an idea, I read my last chapter of ‘let’s be 16 again’ and it popped an idea in my head. I have ideas for two more chapters. So I will write 2 more chapters or maybe more when more ideas pop in my head. I hope you will enjoy it 🙈 have a nice day

title: Avengers 4 title reveal to new characters, Kevin Feige talks future of Marvel Cinematic Universe | hollywood
body:
Avengers 4 title reveal to new characters, Kevin Feige talks future of Marvel Cinematic Universe | hollywood

[ad_1]

As Marvel prepares for the release of their latest superhero film, Ant-Man and the Wasp, the questions on everyone’s minds have less to do with the adventures of Scott Lang and more to do with the future of the Marvel Cinematic Universe, especially after the blockbuster success of Avengers: Infinity War. Doing the press rounds, Marvel chief Kevin Feige couldn’t avoid fielding questions…

This summer our college-aged son and I are watching the Marvel Avenger movies in order. I’ve watched most of them, but not in order, and as of this writing, we just finished The Avengers. summary: Day 27 of #lgbt #pridemonth #sketchdaily brings us Karolina Dean, briefly known as Lucy in the Sky from Marvels...
caption:
Day 27 of #lgbt #pridemonth #sketchdaily brings us Karolina Dean, briefly known as Lucy in the Sky from Marvels Runaways

Created by Brian K Vaughan and Adrian Alphona, currently appearing in the fabulous Runaways series by Rainbow Rowell and Kris Anka

Karolina can currently be seen in the Hulu tv show, as played by Virginia Gardner. I’m really enjoying the tv show so far!

Damn I need to go back and reread my original Runaways digests right now…
